    "long_instructions": "### Add More Layers \r\n\r\nJesse, the music producer, loves what you've done with the beats to Sabrina's chorus. They're looking for more sounds to layer into each vocal and beat combination you made. \r\n\r\n**Try this:** \r\n- Use a `play together` block around each beat you added. Then, add more sounds like bass and instruments to create a fuller sound in each measure. ",
